OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCBI boss 'shocked' at      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffiring over misconduct     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fclaims                     
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The boss of one of the UK's largest    
OL,6, business groups has been fired over    
OL,7, complaints about his behaviour at work.
OL,9,FTony Danker, who will leave the        
OL,10,FConfederation of British Industry (CBI)
OL,11,Ffollowing an investigation over his    
OL,12,Fconduct towards several employees, said
OL,13,Fhe was "shocked" by the sacking.       
OL,15,FThree other CBI employees have also    
OL,16,Fbeen suspended "pending further        
OL,17,Finvestigation into a number of ongoing 
OL,18,Fallegations", the group said.          
OL,20,FIt is also liaising with the police.   
